### ============================================================
### AI 服装素材库 & 悬浮对话框 HTTP 测试
### ============================================================

### 1. 分页查询素材库（所有类型）
GET http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer test1

### 2. 分页查询模特库（仅含模特）
GET http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=20&isModel=true&modelBodyType=slim
Authorization: Bearer test1

### 3. 按关键词搜索
GET http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&keyword=连衣裙&sourceType=fashion_show
Authorization: Bearer test1

### 4. 素材详情（含模特特征）
GET http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/detail?id=1
Authorization: Bearer test1

### 5. 素材库统计
GET http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/stats
Authorization: Bearer test1

### 6. 查询全部采集源
GET http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/sources
Authorization: Bearer test1

### 7. 查询时装秀采集源
GET http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/sources?sourceType=fashion_show
Authorization: Bearer test1

### 8. 触发异步采集（全部 active 来源）
POST http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/collect
Authorization: Bearer test1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "limitPerSource": 20,
  "async": true
}

### 9. 触发同步采集（单个来源）
POST http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/collect
Authorization: Bearer test1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceId": "vogue_runway",
  "limitPerSource": 10,
  "async": false
}

### 10. AI 悬浮对话框 - 首页
POST http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/page-chat
Authorization: Bearer test1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pageName": "home",
  "message": "我想去看模特库"
}

### 11. AI 悬浮对话框 - 模特库（触发筛选行动）
POST http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/page-chat
Authorization: Bearer test1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pageName": "model_library",
  "message": "帮我找一个高挑苗条的模特",
  "minimized": false,
  "positionX": 30,
  "positionY": 150
}

### 12. AI 悬浮对话框 - 设计工作室（触发颜色修改）
POST http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/page-chat
Authorization: Bearer test1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pageName": "design_studio",
  "message": "改成红色，再生成3D"
}

### 13. AI 悬浮对话框 - 3D 预览页面
POST http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/page-chat
Authorization: Bearer test1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pageName": "3d_viewer",
  "message": "旋转360度看看，然后导出OBJ"
}

### 14. 更新悬浮窗状态（最小化到角落）
PUT http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/assistant-state?pageName=model_library&minimized=true&x=10&y=10
Authorization: Bearer test1

### 15. 恢复悬浮窗
PUT http://localhost:48080/admin-api/ai/fashion/library/assistant-state?pageName=model_library&minimized=false&x=30&y=150
Authorization: Bearer test1
